reviews.review_text: Excellent Sound I'm giving this 5 stars just for the sound.  Can't imagine it being much better.

Excellent Bird Song I attended this show.

Bird Song is truly exploratory and spectacular.  There is a whole lot of great music from this show, and the Rain encore is a great capper to top it off.

'92 Dark Star Now this is a great show. The percussion during Crazy Fingers is amazing, in fact the drummers are outstanding throughout. Dark Star and a Rain encore make this show a unique one for me. Great matrix recording, sounds great.

what a blunder Was at the show on the 11th. Drove to the Coliseum parking lot and hung out until the show started then drove home to So Cal, to attend my fiance's (and mine) wedding shower.  Many a time We would banzai home after a show, but this time we had to be "fresh and chipper".  What a blow-it.  Should have seen the mother-in-law problems coming.  Married 4 year and 362 days. (just short of 5 years and Calif mandatory spouse support).
Great Sound ! Turn it up ! Cool Bird Song & Rain... All Good !

It just gets better!! Man, beautiful.... (listening to Rain now)... I am so happy to hear this... Words cant express my gratitude for this... Great sound. I was 11 in 92', but hearing this show, I close my eyes, and I'm there... Great quality, and thanx again!!!
- Parts of this are excellent, and I'm almost rating it a 5. The recording quality is certainly top-notch. It's a bit loose & lacking in dynamic tension between chaos and focus, but what sound!
